# Global Azure Bootcamp CDMX 2017 
These guide will help speakers when delivering this materials. There are some notes in the decks, but this will provide a broader view of how the material was put together.

The Global Azure Bootcamp is a collection of lectures, content and hands on labs that is intended to provide attendees with a jumpstart to Azure development.


## Getting prepared to deliver ##
* It is recommended that the speaker works through the Hands-On-Labs before the session. 

* Azure subscription: 
    To run the demos and perform the hands-on-labs, an Azure subscription is necessary.  You can sign up for a free trial or ask for Azure Pass)

    
